00:10:35.100 --> 00:10:42.500
If you have the lyrics
sheet in front of you,

00:10:42.500 --> 00:10:48.400
it's self-evident.&nbsp; For
those of you who don't,

00:10:48.400 --> 00:10:55.067
the guy's just come back
from war.&nbsp; He's wondering,

00:10:55.067 --> 00:10:56.200
if he's reading
the newspaper,

00:10:56.200 --> 00:10:57.200
if what he's
reading is true,

00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:58.300
and he's talking
about civil rights here,

00:10:58.300 --> 00:11:01.267
of things actually getting
better.&nbsp; Can't find a job

00:11:01.267 --> 00:11:03.700
though, money is tight.&nbsp;
"I don't understand what's

00:11:03.700 --> 00:11:07.967
