And then just wondering,

00:11:07.967 --> 00:11:10.500
you know, are they still
doing stuff they used to do,

00:11:10.500 --> 00:11:14.167
going to the dances?&nbsp; Do you
think anybody has a chance

00:11:14.167 --> 00:11:17.100
to succeed, in this case, a
ball club?&nbsp; "I want to know

00:11:17.100 --> 00:11:20.167
what's going on, what's
happening."&nbsp; Someone who's

00:11:20.167 --> 00:11:23.700
lost and trying to
find his way.&nbsp; Very soon,

00:11:23.700 --> 00:11:25.300
you get an answer
in the same album,

00:11:25.300 --> 00:11:29.700
in the song "Inner City
Blues."&nbsp; Harkening back to

00:11:29.700 --> 00:11:32.300
